metadata.name: Rhenium Founders Pass
metadata.description:
Blue Chip NFT Lottery is the very first NFT lottery project in the Metaverse and NFT space. Blue Chip NFT Lottery offers four types of Founders passes which allows holders to receive airdropped lottery tickets to win various NFTs, $WRLD airdrops, and much more. 
Each of the four Founders pass has a limited quantity and rarity.
